*German: [[Floß]] ''n'' (1), [[Schlauchboot]] ''n'' (2)
*Dutch [[vlot]] ''n'' (1)
*Russian: [[плот]] (plot) ''m'' (1)

===Verb===
'''to raft''' ('''rafts''', '''rafted''', '''rafting'''
#''(transitive)'' to [[convey]] on a raft
#''(transitive)'' to [[make]] [[into]] a raft
#''(intransitive)'' to [[travel]] by raft
===Related terms===
*[[rafter]]
*[[whitewater rafting]]

